        @{b} have you already been disgruntled because ...@{ub}

            * the Workbench does not fit your needs

            * you may not create an icon-link by mouseclick
              for a program or file that is physically stored
              on one of your CDROMs ?

            * there is no lean and good filemanager that you
              may call on the fingertip ?

            * ButtonBars should be more than only a dump tool
              for launching programs


        @{" > " link Main2} @{b} or because ... @{ub}


        @{i}Please, note, that if you would have Locale-Prefs
        set to 'deutsch', now a german guide would have been
        started automatically by the MARInA Installer!@{ui}

        You click one Icon, the Installer does the rest...

