@Node Main3 "MARInA, ©'1998 by Thomas Neidhardt"

        @{b}MARInA Wizards@{ub}

        ©'98 Thomas Neidhardt, 91058 Erlangen, GERMANY
____________________________________________________________________

        @{b}MARInA daily Workflow-Wizards:@{ub}

         * The Standard WB finally gets the extension which it
           should have deserved long ago. Fully integrated by
           ToolManager-Menu and Keyboard-Shortcuts. Fully integrated
           System-Manual Server included.

         * Icon-Links for Programs and Multimedia-Files that are
           located on not actually mounted devices (such as CDROMS)
           may be easily created in any desired direcotry
           on Harddisk.

         * Just by "FingerTip" the "On the Fly" MARInA-FileManager
           will be at your disposal in every Application. Comfortable
           File-Duplicates-Information when copying or moving Files.

         * Shell- or Commandline Inputs will from now on only be
           necessary in special situations (e.g.: Develpment).

         * The MARInA FileManager may be second only by other
           FileManagers (RO, DirWork, ...) if huge File-Copy or
           -Move Operations are to be scheduled.


         @{" > " link MARInA_install.Guide/Main} @{b} MARInA - the easy going ... @{ub}

____________________________________________________________________
@ENDNODE
